---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="DMCA Policy - TribleTunes"
  description="TribleTunes DMCA Policy - Information on intellectual property respect, counter-notifications, and filing a copyright infringement claim."
  keywords="DMCA policy, copyright infringement, music copyright, TribleTunes DMCA, report copyright"
>
  <style slot="head">
    /* INFO CARD */
    .info-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: clamp(10px, 2vw, 15px);
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 30px);
      margin: clamp(20px, 3vh, 30px) 0;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.3rem);
      color: var(--accent-color);
      margin-bottom: clamp(12px, 2vh, 15px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .info-card h3 ion-icon {
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
    }

    .info-card p,
    .info-card ul {
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: clamp(10px, 2vh, 15px);
    }

    .info-card ul {
      padding-left: clamp(20px, 4vw, 30px);
    }

    .info-card li {
      margin-bottom: clamp(8px, 1.5vh, 10px);
    }

    .info-card strong {
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    /* CONTACT INFO BOX */
    .contact-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-color), #ec4899);
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 30px);
      border-radius: clamp(12px, 2vw, 20px);
      margin: clamp(25px, 4vh, 40px) 0;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
    }

    .contact-box h3 {
      color: white;
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
      margin-bottom: clamp(12px, 2vh, 15px);
    }

    .contact-box p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
      margin-bottom: clamp(15px, 2.5vh, 20px);
    }

    .contact-box a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: clamp(10px, 2vh, 12px) clamp(20px, 3vw, 28px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: clamp(20px, 4vw, 30px);
      display: inline-block;
      transition: var(--transition);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .contact-box a:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* FANCY HR LINES */
    hr.fancy-line {
      border: 0;
      height: clamp(2px, 0.3vh, 3px);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent-color), transparent);
      margin: clamp(30px, 5vh, 50px) auto;
      border-radius: 5px;
      max-width: min(600px, 80%);
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- DMCA SECTION -->
  <section id="dmca">
    <h2 class="section-title">DMCA Policy</h2>
    <h3 class="section-subtitle">Digital Millennium Copyright Act</h3>

    <p class="section-text">
      TribleTunes respects the intellectual property rights of others and expects our users to do the same. In
      accordance with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA), we will respond promptly to claims of copyright
      infringement committed using our platform.
    </p>

    <hr class="fancy-line">

    <div class="info-card">
      <h3><ion-icon name="shield-checkmark-outline"></ion-icon> Copyright Respect</h3>
      <p>
        We take copyright infringement seriously. All content on TribleTunes is created with proper permissions and
        licenses from artists and rights holders. If you believe any content on our platform infringes your copyright,
        please follow the procedure outlined below.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-card">
      <h3><ion-icon name="document-text-outline"></ion-icon> Filing a DMCA Notice</h3>
      <p>
        If you are a copyright owner (or authorized to act on behalf of one) and believe that content on TribleTunes
        infringes your copyright, please submit a written notice with the following information:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identification of the copyrighted work:</strong> A description of the copyrighted work that you
          claim has been infringed.</li>
        <li><strong>Identification of the infringing material:</strong> The URL or specific location on our platform
          where the allegedly infringing material is located.</li>
        <li><strong>Your contact information:</strong> Your name, address, telephone number, and email address.</li>
        <li><strong>Statement of good faith:</strong> A statement that you have a good faith belief that the disputed
          use is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.</li>
        <li><strong>Statement of accuracy:</strong> A statement, under penalty of perjury, that the information in your
          notice is accurate and that you are the copyright owner or authorized to act on their behalf.</li>
        <li><strong>Your signature:</strong> A physical or electronic signature of the copyright owner or a person
          authorized to act on their behalf.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="info-card">
      <h3><ion-icon name="checkmark-circle-outline"></ion-icon> Counter-Notification</h3>
      <p>
        If you believe that material you posted was removed or access to it was disabled by mistake or
        misidentification, you may file a counter-notification. Your counter-notification must include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Identification of the material that has been removed or disabled.</li>
        <li>Your name, address, telephone number, and email address.</li>
        <li>A statement under penalty of perjury that you have a good faith belief that the material was removed or
          disabled as a result of mistake or misidentification.</li>
        <li>A statement that you consent to the jurisdiction of the Federal District Court for the judicial district in
          which your address is located.</li>
        <li>Your physical or electronic signature.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="info-card">
      <h3><ion-icon name="time-outline"></ion-icon> Response Time</h3>
      <p>
        Upon receipt of a valid DMCA notice, we will take the following actions:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Remove or disable access to the allegedly infringing material.</li>
        <li>Notify the user who posted the material that it has been removed or disabled.</li>
        <li>Investigate the claim and take appropriate action, which may include termination of repeat infringers'
          accounts.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We aim to respond to all valid DMCA notices within 48-72 hours.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-card">
      <h3><ion-icon name="warning-outline"></ion-icon> Repeat Infringers</h3>
      <p>
        TribleTunes maintains a policy of terminating, in appropriate circumstances, accounts of users who are repeat
        infringers. We reserve the right to terminate access to the platform for any user who repeatedly infringes the
        copyrights of others.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-box">
      <h3>Send Your DMCA Notice</h3>
      <p>
        Please send all DMCA notices and counter-notifications to our designated copyright agent via email:
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:contact@tribletunes.com">dmca@tribletunes.com</a>
    </div>

    <p class="section-text" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2025
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
